<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 04 at 11:44PM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Brief Period of Heavy Snow...
A band of moderate to heavy snow is currently moving across the
area. Visibilities below one half mile and snowfall rates of up to
two inches per hour are possible for a brief period tonight.
Anyone travelling is urged to slow down, be prepared for rapid
changes in conditions, and leave plenty of stopping distance.</description>
